object.customQuery:
SELECT
cd.ClaimantKey as ClaimantKey,
cd.ClaimantDetailHashKey as ClaimantDetailHashKey,
cd.RowEffStartDt as RowEffStartDt,
cd.ClaimID as ClaimID,
cd.ClaimantId as ClaimantId,
cd.RowEffEndDt as RowEffEndDt,cd.ClaimSystemId as ClaimSystemId
 FROM dbo.ClaimantDetail  cd
where cd.RowEffEndDt='9999-12-31'---

object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT d.emailaddr as EmailAddr,  b.id as Id, b.systemid as SystemId
FROM dbo.claimant_stg b
         INNER JOIN dbo.claim_stg a on a.id = b.parentid
    and a.systemid = b.systemid
         INNER JOIN dbo.partyinfo_stg c ON b.id = c.parentid
    AND b.systemid = c.systemid
         INNER JOIN dbo.emailinfo_stg d ON c.id = d.parentid
    AND c.systemid = d.systemid
WHERE a.cmmcontainer = 'Claim'
  AND a.typecd = 'Claim'
  AND b.cmmcontainer = 'Claim'
  AND c.cmmcontainer = 'Claim'
  AND d.cmmcontainer = 'Claim'
  AND c.partytypecd = 'ClaimantParty'
  AND d.emailtypecd = 'ClaimantEmail'
